{{Quote|It is a legend in the medical establishment. An ancient medicine that made bacta look no more potent than a strong glass of lum. But it has not grown wild for millennia.|[[Seeqov Thranx]] describing Kolcta|<ref name="Thyferra: Bacta Basics">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20031106thyferra|text=Thyferra: Bacta Basics|int=Thyferra: Bacta Basics}}</ref>}}
'''Kolcta''', a rare hybrid of [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] and [[Kolto/Legends|kolto]], was an extremely powerful curative agent. The fluid was so scarce that full submersion was near impractical, so it was usually sold and applied as a simple soaked cloth. Kolcta treatment could help reattach severed limbs, heal almost any kind of wound and, if ingested, counter the effects of aging.

